[normal]sing clearanc
[normal]es
[normal] to see if on average 
[normal]a lo
[normal]wer proportion of drivers 
[normal]pass
[normal] 
[normal]too close
[normal].
[normal] If a change in driving culture oc
[normal]curs with more consideration given to 
[normal]c
[normal]yclists would need assessing
[normal]. 
[normal]Accident data for all road users can be evaluated against the trends. 
